{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"79b7696218","title":"可在先头阻止李弥余程万部向越南缅甸前进","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"49b2c7a663","index":0,"year":1949,"month":12,"day":29,"articleId":"79b7696218"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"9c0013443a","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"79b7696218","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"少奇，即刘少奇。"},{"id":"8d8764e044","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"79b7696218","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘邓，指刘伯承、邓小平，当时分别任第二野战军司令员和政治委员。"},{"id":"35824fdea9","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"79b7696218","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"卢汉，原任国民党云南省政府主席、国民党军云南绥靖公署主任。1949年12月9日率部在昆明起义。"},{"id":"435d40b415","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"79b7696218","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李弥、余程万，当时分别任国民党军第八军军长和第二十六军军长。此时，这两个军正向越南、缅甸边境出逃。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9d0a54568d","type":"title","text":"可在先头阻止李弥余程万部向越南细甸前进","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"79b7696218"},{"id":"9c0013443a","type":"paragraph","text":"少奇\"同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"79b7696218"},{"id":"8d8764e044","type":"paragraph","text":"请告刘邓转知卢汉回及云南我军，只可在季弥、余程方可之先头阻止其向越、细前进，不可向其后尾威肠或追击，以免该敌过早退入越南。卢汉及我军均应向该敌进行政治工作，策动该敌起义。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"79b7696218"},{"id":"35824fdea9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"79b7696218"},{"id":"435d40b415","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月二十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"79b7696218"}],"page":{"id":"a24a3c93e5","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"79b7696218","start":105,"end":105}}}},"__N_SSG":true}